import React from 'react' import './Analysis.css' import ReactHtmlParser from 'react-html-parser' const Article = (props) => { const article = props.location.state.article console.log(props.article) console.log(article) return(
{article.title && <>
{article.title}
{article.type} - By: {article.author} - {`${article.date.substring(4, 6)}/${article.date.substring(6, 8)}/${article.date.substring(0, 4)}`}

{ReactHtmlParser(article.body)}
}
) } export default Article
